{"name": "lcls", "metadata": {"name": "lcls", "version": "1.0.4", "classifiers": [], "home_page": "https://github.com/pouya-eghbali/lc", "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["sty", "ruamel.yaml"], "summary": "lc is ls but with colors and icons.", "upload_time": 1734884209}, "documentation": ["# lc\n\n`lc` is `ls` but with colors and icons.\n\n![lc screenshot](https://github.com/pouya-eghbali/lc/raw/master/lc.png)\n\n## Install\n\nTo install do\n\n```\npip install lcls\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nThe executable is named `lcls` to prevent conflicts with `ls` and mono `lc`, you can make an alias and name it however you want.\n\n```\nlcls -[al] [directory]\n```\n\nMultiple directories can be provided. Currently lc recognizes `-a` and `-l` options.\nDirectory is optional (defaults to current working directory)\n\n## Configuration\n\n`lc` first tries to read `~/.lc.rules.yaml` and if it fails it will load the default configuration from where it is installed.\n\nTo customize icons and colors you can copy `.lc.rules.yaml` to your home folder and modify its contents.\n\nFor color, either provide a [number (8bit color number)](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ANSI_escape_code#8-bit),\na list of numbers (rgb), or the color name.\n\n## Dependencies\n\nYou need nerd fonts (or equivalent) to make this work properly. Python dependencies are `sty` and `ruamel.yaml`\n"], "modules": [{"name": "lcls", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "lcls.get_rules", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lcls.colorize", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "color", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "icon", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "file", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lcls.chunks", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "l", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "n", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lcls.get_terminal_size", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "fallback", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lcls.get_table_size", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "table", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lcls.lpad_equal", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "items", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lcls.num2sym", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "num", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lcls.get_perm", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "file", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lcls.print_with_options", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "files", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "colorized_files", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "size", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "options", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lcls.is_hidden", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "directory", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "filename", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lcls.has_hidden_attribute", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "filepath", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "lcls.main", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "lcls.perm_map", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "lcls.datetime", "xref": {"fqname": "datetime.datetime", "project": null}}, {"name": "lcls.YAML", "xref": {"fqname": "ruamel.yaml.YAML", "project": null}}]}]}